---
title: Italian Ribollita with Kale, Italian Sausage and Crispy Croutons
description: Our take on the beloved ribollita is ideal for this time of year. Italian sausage adds intense flavour to the dish, but our favourite addition is the chili flakes — just a pinch adds enough heat to warm us up!
